jQuery is required!

Download the plugin, extract to plugins directory

Enable the plugin in ProjectConfiguration
  public function setup()
  {
    $this->enablePlugins(
      'sfPropelPlugin',
      'dcI18NTranslatorPlugin'
  }

Enable the module in apps/app/config/settings.yml
    enabled_modules:      [default, translator ]

Change the xml permission to
    chmod o+w messages.xml


the URI to the xml must show with this!
i18n/es/messages.xml


Usage

go to app/translator and voila!
